{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"aside","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-3\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">El <strong>elemento HTML <code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></strong> representa una sección de una página que consiste en contenido que está indirectamente relacionado con el contenido principal del documento.</span></span> <span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-4\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Estas secciones son a menudo representadas como barras laterales o como inserciones y contienen una explicación al margen como una definición de glosario, elementos relacionados indirectamente, como publicidad, la biografía del autor, o en aplicaciones web, la información de perfil o enlaces a blogs relacionados.</span></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><em><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-5\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Notas de uso:</span></span></em></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-6\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">No utilices el elemento <code>&lt;aside&gt;</code> para etiquetar texto entre paréntesis, ya que este tipo de texto se considera parte del flujo principal.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contexto_de_uso","title":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-7\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Contexto de uso</span></span>","isH3":true,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-8\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Contenido permitido</span></span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"en/HTML/Content categories#flow content\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-9\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Contenido dinámico</span></span></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-10\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Omisión de etiquetas</span></span></td>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-11\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-ph-missing goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Ninguna, tanto la etiqueta inicial y la etiqueta de cierre son obligatorias</span></span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-12\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Elementos primarios permitidos</span></span></td>\n   <td>\n    <p><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-13\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-97 goog-gtc-ph-missing goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Cualquier elemento que acepte&nbsp;contenido dinámico.</span></span> <span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-14\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-ph-missing goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Ten en cuenta que un elemento &lt;aside&gt; no debe ser un descendiente de un elemento <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>.</span></span></p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-15\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Documento normativo</span></span></td>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/sections.html#the-aside-element\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-16\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">HTML 5, sección 4.4.5</span></span></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>","titleAsText":"Contexto de uso"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"<span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-17\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Atributos</span></span>","isH3":true,"content":"<p><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-18\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-ph-missing goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Este elemento no tiene atributos que no sean los <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Global_attributes\" title=\"../../../../en/HTML/global attributes\">atributos globales</a>, comunes a todos los elementos.</span></span></p>\n\n<div id=\"section_3\">\n<div id=\"section_3\">\n<h3 class=\"editable\" id=\"interfaz_dom\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-19\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Interfaz DOM</span></span></h3>\n\n<p><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-20\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-ph-missing goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Este elemento implementa la interfaz </span></span><code><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/element\" title=\"en/DOM/element\">HTMLElement</a></code><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-20\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-ph-missing goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">.</span></span></p>\n\n<h3 id=\"consulta_también\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-21\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-tm goog-gtc-from-tm-score-100 goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Consulta también</span></span></h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-22\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-human goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\">Otros elementos relacionados con esta sección: <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>;</span></span></li>\n <li class=\"last\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-unit\" id=\"goog-gtc-unit-23\"><span class=\"goog-gtc-from-mt goog-gtc-translatable\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"deki-ns current\" href=\"/en-US/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"en/Sections and Outlines of an HTML5 document\">Secciones y líneas generales de un documento HTML 5</a> .</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p></p>","titleAsText":"Atributos"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"El elemento HTML <aside> representa una sección de una página que consiste en contenido que está indirectamente relacionado con el contenido principal del documento. Estas secciones son a menudo representadas como barras laterales o como inserciones y contienen una explicación al margen como una definición de glosario, elementos relacionados indirectamente, como publicidad, la biografía del autor, o en aplicaciones web, la información de perfil o enlaces a blogs relacionados.","popularity":0.0015,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<aside>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<aside>: The Aside element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<aside> : l'élément aparté","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<aside>: 余談要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<aside>: 별도 구획 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<aside>","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<aside>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<aside>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<aside>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/html/element/aside","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/html/element/aside/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Lenguaje de etiquetas de hipertexto"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Referencia de Elementos HTML"},